            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>
                <b>Auto</b>
                <b>Fit</b>
              </entry>
              <entry>Automatically sizes the image to fit the paper size you selected</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>
                <b>Custom</b>
                <b>100%</b>and other conversions</entry>
              <entry>Displays the amount to re-size the original. Change the amount by adjusting the <b>Custom Size</b>setting.</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
